{"id": 1321, "genre": 1000, "title": "【好奇心x通用汽车】冬天来了，哪些额外花销让你更头痛？", "description": "这是一个有着（冰冷）温度的投票。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6494, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161110143740H1K4MdOhRYy2o53x.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-13T16:19:18Z", "questions": [{"id": 1346, "title": "【好奇心x通用汽车】冬天来了，哪些额外花销让你更头痛？", "content": "【好奇心x通用】冬天来了，哪些额外花销让你更头痛？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 132155, "content": "更新取暖设备，种草油汀、暖被炉到暖风机", "image": "img/option/option/20161109224353jGzrL3w2D1omSK8X.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 132156, "content": "把空调开到最热，月底看到电费账单哭了", "image": "img/option/option/20161109214317bWprh8x3oweZMIkR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 132162, "content": "汽车加油更加频繁了，油耗也是个负担", "image": "img/option/option/20161110154658jsJ3PeIGlhdFB0cA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 132158, "content": "服装咬牙升级，把羊绒、加拿大鹅、貂提上日程", "image": "img/option/option/20161109214351DcMmKJklhFRyEUBs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 132159, "content": "手套、围巾、帽子、靴子，每件都消费升级一下，加起来就……", "image": "img/option/option/20161109214421V4pex1Cv6kSl9Rg0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 132157, "content": "不得了，每天都想约人吃饭，吃火锅", "image": "img/option/option/20161109214329DXle5xzUfcQIuvCY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 132163, "content": "其实最贵的是空净器、口罩、防毒面具", "image": "img/option/option/20161109214443dpc6CMEHiATswLSW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 133656, "content": "夏天用的乳液不够滋润了，新买个面霜眼霜什么的", "image": "img/option/option/20161114104235FMX4sYKTwnfNl7Gr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 133657, "content": "冷得根本不想出门买菜，天天外卖", "image": "img/option/option/20161114104518cYRBkbHx9aJC5pfP.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 133658, "content": "圣诞新年的限定款，也不知道为啥就买了", "image": "img/option/option/20161114104703Nt7sJn8fz0Euv1BF.GIF", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 133659, "content": "贴完秋膘，是时候减减肥了，买个健身卡什么的", "image": "img/option/option/20161114104839bMGwz0muJnTY2joF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}